testcase.name: CosmosDBSinkSettings should throws an exception if endpoint is empty
CosmosDBSinkSettings should throws an exception if masterkey is empty
CosmosDBSinkSettings should throws an exception if database is empty
CosmosDBSinkSettings should throws an exception if collection is empty
CosmosDBSinkSettings should throws an exception if topic name is empty
CosmosDBSinkSettings should createDatabase && createCollection should be false if no setting provided
CosmosDBSinkSettings should set createDatabase flag if value is set to true
CosmosDBSinkSettings should set createCollection flag if value is set to true
CosmosDBSinkSettings should should throw an exception if createDatabase is neither "true" or "false
CosmosDBSinkSettings should should throw an exception if createCollection is neither "true" or "false
